                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word God is not rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works</desc>
                  <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#121v" facs="124">fols. 121v, </locus> (Ps. 150), <locus target="#131v #132r #132v" facs="134 134 135">131v, 132r, 132v</locus> (tenth biblical canticle)</desc>
